open the NDTS from the directory C:\windows\NTDS\NTDS.DIT- Rename this to old

Go to C drive and locate the mounted drive
Open and go to windows\ntds
Copy the NTDS.DIT
Paste it to C:\windows\NTDS\

Start NTDS
net start NTDS
